<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>中国新闻|今日突发新闻|路透社</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/</link><description>Reuters.com 是您获取最新中国新闻故事和时事的在线来源，确保我们的读者及时了解任何突发新闻动态 - RSSHub 用爱制作(https://github.com/DIYgod/RSSHub)</description><lastBuildDate>Thu, 20 Jun 2024 09:14:24 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>泰国在十月峰会上考虑加入金砖国家并开始申请加入经合组织</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/thailand-eyes-brics-membership-october-summit-begins-oecd-application-2024-06-20/</link><description>泰国外交部官员周四表示，泰国希望在十月份于俄罗斯举行的金砖国家峰会上成为新兴经济体金砖国家集团的成员。</description><pubDate>Thu, 20 Jun 2024 08:22:32 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/thailand-eyes-brics-membership-october-summit-begins-oecd-application-2024-06-20/</guid></item><item><title>中国称达赖喇嘛必须“彻底纠正”他的政治观点</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/china-says-dalai-lama-must-thoroughly-correct-his-political-views-2024-06-20/</link><description>中国外交部周四表示，西藏精神领袖达赖喇嘛必须“彻底纠正”他的政治观点，作为与中国中央政府恢复接触的条件。</description><pubDate>Thu, 20 Jun 2024 08:07:11 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/china-says-dalai-lama-must-thoroughly-correct-his-political-views-2024-06-20/</guid></item><item><title>官员称，印度对中国时隔四年恢复客运航班的呼吁置之不理</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/india-shuns-chinas-calls-resume-passenger-flights-after-4-years-officials-say-2024-06-20/</link><description>官员们表示，中国正在敦促印度在中断四年后重新启动直航客运航班，但新德里方面予以抵制，因为边界争端继续影响着世界上两个人口最多国家之间的关系。</description><pubDate>Thu, 20 Jun 2024 08:04:21 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/india-shuns-chinas-calls-resume-passenger-flights-after-4-years-officials-say-2024-06-20/</guid></item><item><title>中国召开重要全会旨在解决数十年之久的税收收入失衡问题</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/chinas-key-plenum-aims-fix-decades-old-tax-revenue-imbalance-2024-06-20/</link><description>政策顾问表示，长期吹捧的中国税收制度改革将侧重于允许地方政府保留更多财政收入，市场普遍认为这是消除金融稳定面临的直接威胁的重要一步。</description><pubDate>Thu, 20 Jun 2024 08:04:09 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/chinas-key-plenum-aims-fix-decades-old-tax-revenue-imbalance-2024-06-20/</guid></item><item><title>官员称中国可能对欧盟进口猪肉采取反倾销措施</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/china-may-take-anti-dumping-measures-against-eu-pork-imports-official-says-2024-06-20/</link><description>中国商务部周四表示，作为自 6 月 17 日开始的为期一年的调查的一部分，中国可能对从欧盟进口的猪肉实施临时反倾销措施。</description><pubDate>Thu, 20 Jun 2024 08:02:03 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/china-may-take-anti-dumping-measures-against-eu-pork-imports-official-says-2024-06-20/</guid></item><item><title>中国表示欧盟电动汽车调查要求提供的信息“史无前例”</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/china-says-information-requested-by-eu-electric-vehicle-probe-unprecedented-2024-06-20/</link><description>中国商务部周四表示，欧盟对中国新能源汽车调查要求提供的信息种类、范围和数量“史无前例”。</description><pubDate>Thu, 20 Jun 2024 07:36:05 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/china-says-information-requested-by-eu-electric-vehicle-probe-unprecedented-2024-06-20/</guid></item><item><title>中国倾销调查考验西班牙养猪户的韧性</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/chinas-dumping-probe-another-test-resilience-spains-pig-farmers-2024-06-20/</link><description>本周，在对中国电动汽车征收关税后，中国对欧盟猪肉进口展开倾销调查，这让西班牙的养猪户措手不及，但该行业已显示出其韧性，并且远没有欧盟汽车行业那么脆弱。</description><pubDate>Thu, 20 Jun 2024 06:05:33 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/chinas-dumping-probe-another-test-resilience-spains-pig-farmers-2024-06-20/</guid></item><item><title>中美将举行禁毒合作高层会谈</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/us-china-hold-high-level-talks-anti-narcotics-cooperation-2024-06-20/</link><description>继本周双边工作取得突破、共同打击与毒品有关的重大洗钱行动之后，美国和中国定于周四就反毒品合作举行高层会谈。</description><pubDate>Thu, 20 Jun 2024 05:23:42 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/us-china-hold-high-level-talks-anti-narcotics-cooperation-2024-06-20/</guid></item><item><title>朝鲜、俄罗斯具有里程碑意义的战略伙伴关系条约的要点</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/key-points-north-korea-russia-landmark-strategic-partnership-treaty-2024-06-20/</link><description>朝鲜官方媒体周四公布了朝鲜领导人金正恩和俄罗斯总统普京一天前签署的共同防御协议的全文，金正恩表示，该协议将把双边关系提升为类似于“联盟”的程度。</description><pubDate>Thu, 20 Jun 2024 05:20:06 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/key-points-north-korea-russia-landmark-strategic-partnership-treaty-2024-06-20/</guid></item><item><title>腾讯《地下城与勇士》游戏从部分 Android 应用商店下架</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/tencents-dungeon-fighter-game-pulled-some-android-app-stores-2024-06-20/</link><description>腾讯表示，由于合同已到期，腾讯将从周四起将其热门手机游戏《地下城与勇士》（DnF Mobile）从选定的 Android 应用商店下架。</description><pubDate>Thu, 20 Jun 2024 05:11:28 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/tencents-dungeon-fighter-game-pulled-some-android-app-stores-2024-06-20/</guid></item><item><title>河流水位上涨威胁更多洪水，降雨袭击中国南方</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/environment/rains-lash-southern-china-rising-rivers-threaten-more-flooding-2024-06-20/</link><description>中国南方连日来的暴雨、山洪和山体滑坡迫使当局制定应急计划，因为河水上涨有进一步泛滥的危险，可能会扰乱数百万人的生活。</description><pubDate>Thu, 20 Jun 2024 04:24:48 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/environment/rains-lash-southern-china-rising-rivers-threaten-more-flooding-2024-06-20/</guid></item><item><title>德国在韩国看到了志同道合的贸易盟友</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/germany-sees-like-minded-trade-ally-south-korea-2024-06-20/</link><description>德国经济部长周四抵达韩国，这是其亚洲之行的第一站，寻求加深与该地区第四大经济体的关系，柏林旨在“降低”对华贸易风险。</description><pubDate>Thu, 20 Jun 2024 04:05:33 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/germany-sees-like-minded-trade-ally-south-korea-2024-06-20/</guid></item><item><title>亚洲股市稳定，英国央行会议前英镑谨慎行事</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-markets-wrapup-1-2024-06-20/</link><description>亚洲股市周四稍作喘息，徘徊在两年来最高点附近，交易员等待更多美国政策线索，而英镑在英国央行会议之前保持稳定，预计利率将保持不变。</description><pubDate>Thu, 20 Jun 2024 02:38:58 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-markets-wrapup-1-2024-06-20/</guid></item><item><title>繁忙的央行日美元上涨，瑞士法郎下跌</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/currencies/sterling-steady-ahead-boe-decision-dollar-wobbles-against-yen-2024-06-20/</link><description>美元周四上涨，而瑞士法郎下跌，英镑下跌，因为繁忙的一天央行会议让货币交易者保持警惕。</description><pubDate>Thu, 20 Jun 2024 01:30:30 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/currencies/sterling-steady-ahead-boe-decision-dollar-wobbles-against-yen-2024-06-20/</guid></item><item><title>中国人民银行走紧绳子，中国保持基准利率稳定</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/china-leaves-lending-benchmark-rates-unchanged-expected-2024-06-20/</link><description>中国周四维持基准贷款利率不变，符合市场预期。</description><pubDate>Thu, 20 Jun 2024 01:23:01 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/china-leaves-lending-benchmark-rates-unchanged-expected-2024-06-20/</guid></item></channel></rss>